org.paces.Stata.MetaData

Class Variables

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.paces.Stata.MetaData.Variables

  • public class Variables
extends Object
    Class used for Stata's Java API to access the metadata for Stata variables. This class is initialized by the Meta class object which also builds/contains data related to the observation metadata.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    Billy Buchanan
